author: Rob Braxman Tech
description:
We'll discuss the introduction of the new AI Assistant from OpenAI called Operator and compare this to Windows Copilot, Apple Intelligence and we'll see if we can come up with a safe alternative while still taking advantage of the new technology. To do this, we will dissect the differences between the AI Agents and see what makes them tick.
